        "subject": "LU-5530 mdt: Force resent due to large replies.",
        "message": "LU-5530 mdt: Force resent due to large replies.\n\nThis is currently a test only patch to force resending\nof requests as if we have large striping in play which is common\non larger sites, but not in our testing.\n\nEventually this will be a fail_loc, I think, but RIGHT NOW THIS\nIS NOT INTENDED FOR LANDING.\n\nThis also causes a bunch of client reconnections in racer for some\nunknown reason in my testing.\n\nChange-Id: Ibfc131c72b6f810fc7380035268ed47f613989fb\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
